00:01:49.299 --> 00:01:50.500
Thank you, Sister Goddess.

00:02:08.819 --> 00:02:10.539
Girl, you’re a demon.

00:02:11.199 --> 00:02:13.099
The Northern Abyss Glacier is a sacred immortal land.

00:02:13.419 --> 00:02:15.520
The fierce winds and freezing cold are deadly for you.

00:02:15.960 --> 00:02:17.379
Even the Celestial Goddess Tongtian said

00:02:17.580 --> 00:02:19.319
the Lord of the Northern Abyss won’t save him.

00:02:19.620 --> 00:02:21.000
Why bother with this futile effort?

00:02:22.300 --> 00:02:24.520
I won’t abandon Brother Yuanqi.

00:02:31.900 --> 00:02:32.800
