00:04:54.279 --> 00:04:56.300
dare disturb my cultivation?

00:04:58.519 --> 00:04:59.259
Heavenly Lord,

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:01.319
please save Brother Yuanqi!

00:05:02.319 --> 00:05:04.339
I see your sincerity.

00:05:04.720 --> 00:05:06.360
According to the sect’s rules,

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:08.759
only those who bow a hundred times may meet me.

00:05:08.899 --> 00:05:10.800
I appear only when absolutely necessary.

00:05:11.060 --> 00:05:11.720
However,

00:05:12.240 --> 00:05:15.819
I cannot interfere with worldly karma at will.

00:05:16.160 --> 00:05:16.980
Leave at once.

00:05:17.420 --> 00:05:17.800
Heavenly Lord,

00:05:17.800 --> 00:05:19.740
I didn’t expect the legendary Lingbao Heavenly Lord

00:05:19.759 --> 00:05:21.279
to be so powerless.

00:05:23.579 --> 00:05:24.480
What did you say?

00:05:26.560 --> 00:05:28.600
If you can’t save him, aren’t you useless?

00:05:29.319 --> 00:05:30.819
Provocation won’t work on me.

00:05:31.759 --> 00:05:34.220
His cultivation method is not orthodox.

00:05:34.519 --> 00:05:37.079
You should take him away quickly.

00:05:37.240 --> 00:05:38.279
