00:05:44.620 --> 00:05:45.459
that all beings of the Three Realms

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.040
who pass the trial

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:48.279
can receive divine aid.

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:51.459
Why won’t you give him a chance?

00:05:52.439 --> 00:05:54.040
