00:05:55.560 --> 00:05:57.839
Then let’s follow the rules.

00:05:58.180 --> 00:05:58.779
But

00:05:59.399 --> 00:06:01.860
I will decide the content of the trial.

00:06:02.519 --> 00:06:05.519
I will summon the Nine Heavens Thunder Tribulation to strike him.

00:06:05.740 --> 00:06:07.079
He is already gravely injured.

00:06:08.259 --> 00:06:09.600
If he cannot withstand it,

00:06:09.860 --> 00:06:11.180
he will be reduced to ashes.

00:06:12.139 --> 00:06:13.279
Don’t blame me.

00:06:13.379 --> 00:06:13.800
This...

00:06:15.019 --> 00:06:15.980
