00:06:16.160 --> 00:06:17.120
Leave at once.

00:06:19.259 --> 00:06:20.740
Girl, stop making trouble.

00:06:21.180 --> 00:06:22.040
This Nine Heavens Thunder Tribulation

00:06:22.040 --> 00:06:23.779
even a Great Luo Golden Immortal might not survive it.

00:06:24.220 --> 00:06:26.100
Let alone Chen Yuanqi, who is gravely wounded.

00:06:28.279 --> 00:06:28.819
No!

00:06:30.399 --> 00:06:31.040
Heavenly Lord,

00:06:31.759 --> 00:06:32.660
please summon the thunder.

00:06:32.959 --> 00:06:34.439
Brother Yuanqi will definitely endure it!

00:06:35.220 --> 00:06:35.620
You...

00:06:40.259 --> 00:06:41.120
Brother Yuanqi...

00:06:49.300 --> 00:06:50.459
According to the rules,

00:06:50.680 --> 00:06:52.399
if he survives the tribulation,

00:06:52.779 --> 00:06:56.379
he will receive the inheritance of my Northern Abyss Glacier.

00:06:56.959 --> 00:06:58.759
The Nine Heavens Responsive Thunder Art.

00:06:59.540 --> 00:07:01.819
But if he fails,

00:07:02.100 --> 00:07:05.379
his body and soul will be destroyed forever.

00:07:21.079 --> 00:07:22.660
How is that possible?

00:07:23.300 --> 00:07:24.740
This is the Nine Heavens Thunder Tribulation!

00:07:25.060 --> 00:07:27.079
How can a mere mortal withstand it?

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:33.339
The Spirit Hound Clan’s supreme technique allows body and mind to substitute each other.

00:07:33.620 --> 00:07:35.639
You’re actually taking the thunder for Chen Yuanqi?

00:07:36.899 --> 00:07:38.680
Even if your technique is profound,

00:07:39.339 --> 00:07:40.980
you can’t withstand more than three bolts.

00:07:41.500 --> 00:07:43.100
There are over ten bolts here.

00:07:44.160 --> 00:07:45.000
Bai Xiaoqiu...

00:07:45.620 --> 00:07:46.779
Why are you doing this?

00:07:47.259 --> 00:07:47.959
