00:07:59.420 --> 00:08:01.339
charge into the Celestial Origin Academy

00:08:01.980 --> 00:08:03.439
to find my clansmen.

00:08:04.360 --> 00:08:05.319
My life

00:08:05.740 --> 00:08:07.759
has long belonged to Brother Yuanqi.

00:08:08.500 --> 00:08:09.800
We of the Spirit Hound Clan

00:08:10.279 --> 00:08:12.379
may not be clever,

00:08:12.959 --> 00:08:14.019
but we

00:08:14.800 --> 00:08:16.339
always repay kindness,

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:18.660
and always avenge wrongs.

00:08:21.800 --> 00:08:23.139
Don’t flatter yourself.

00:08:23.980 --> 00:08:26.500
Chen Yuanqi only dared to help you because the Celestial Goddess Tongtian protected him.

00:08:27.079 --> 00:08:28.199
That’s why he stood up for you.

00:08:28.579 --> 00:08:29.720
If he knew he would die,

00:08:29.860 --> 00:08:31.160
he might not have entered the Celestial Origin Academy.

00:08:31.160 --> 00:08:32.379
That makes sense.

00:08:32.919 --> 00:08:33.980
Throughout history,

00:08:34.500 --> 00:08:36.059
how many have truly sacrificed themselves for righteousness?

00:08:36.659 --> 00:08:37.919
Very few.

00:08:38.779 --> 00:08:42.639
People are all selfish.

00:08:49.399 --> 00:08:50.159
Xiaoqiu...

00:08:51.240 --> 00:08:52.220
Stop now!

00:08:53.039 --> 00:08:53.679
Chen Yuanqi...

00:08:54.220 --> 00:08:55.440
I advise you to think carefully.

00:08:55.759 --> 00:08:57.620
If she stops channeling her power now,

00:08:58.019 --> 00:08:59.940
you’ll be struck dead by the tribulation instantly.

00:09:03.899 --> 00:09:04.820
