00:11:46.460 --> 00:11:48.860
Even though you've mastered the Nine Heavens Responsive Thunder Art,

00:11:49.419 --> 00:11:51.539
to save your mother, you must go to the Jiang Clan.

00:11:52.279 --> 00:11:54.480
